價值。<br />\n講錢，你識投資，買樓買虛擬貨幣，都賺到錢，但唔係有價值。"},{"pid":"c1520e1c82e3f91d4d5e657888e1534d7108361e","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46978b2c4a8c2bbd1d731b46a154c66c106d9f20","tid":531813,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e78f1d4eb6a95e6dc024b73f041b97894bf504f","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c62962db3c362731afa2b6bb06f62c6f2a1e157f","tid":531813,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"打開部電話望下你個GOOGLE MAP"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:35:12.000Z","msg":"Google Map is Google's <strong>product</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"then? 天文冇用?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:41:57.000Z","msg":"衛星照片，衛星科技 =/= 天文學<br />\n<br />\n衛星離地面1000公點以內<br />\n宇宙講緊930億光年<br />\n太陽系都講緊至少200億公里"},{"pid":"353bdeffb01194c4d96243d101d088fa78c2d2a3","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8e8beed31dd341de05bedfe7755a51e865e031d","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a6859c27f45f7fc95ec39fc877d2d8d45053ecd7","tid":531813,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:25:41.000Z","msg":"點解要用錢嚟衡量?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:40:53.000Z","msg":"唔係錢，而係價值，係社會價值。<br />\n講錢，你識投資，買樓買虛擬貨幣，都賺到錢，但唔係有價值。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"不過知識用黎做應用、研究、教學都叫有價值。<br />\n<br />\n但如果你理科phd， 但做緊的野，係form 6/form 7仔都識做，當然只值10000至20000人工啦。"},{"pid":"0c5143946a8522906e7bef1034d9da3c0a14dad0","tid":531813,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1520e1c82e3f91d4d5e657888e1534d7108361e","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"46978b2c4a8c2bbd1d731b46a154c66c106d9f20","tid":531813,"uid":37375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e78f1d4eb6a95e6dc024b73f041b97894bf504f","tid":531813,"uid":149978,"like":0,